{"lemma":"قِلادَةٌ","slug":"قِلادَةٌ","root":"ق.ل.د","root_slug":"ق-ل-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ل-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36129"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%90%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pendant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"necklace","examples":[{"text":"تَرْتَدِينَ قِلَادَةً جَمِيلَةً ٱلْيَوْمَ.","english":"You are wearing a beautiful necklace today."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qi.laː.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36129","headword_ar":"قِلَادَةٌ","root":"qld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A necklace; a collar;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is upon the neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is put upon the neck"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a human being, and a horse, and a dog, and a camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bull that is brought as an offering to Mekkeh for sacrifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[see 2,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) Esh-Shiháb observes, in the 'Ináyeh, that the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEaAlapN","text_ar":"فِعَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the case"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2558},{"kind":"text","text":"of a word not an inf. n., denotes a thing that envelops, or that surrounds, another thing; as in the instances of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifaAfapN","text_ar":"لِفَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EimaAmapN","text_ar":"عِمَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdapN","text_ar":"قِلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaAy^idu","text_ar":"قَلَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdN","text_ar":"قِلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also occurs, either as a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdapN","text_ar":"قِلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which case the kesreh and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the pl. are different from the kesreh and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sing., [being the proper characteristics of the pl.,] or as a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdapN","text_ar":"قِلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un. (ISd, L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasobuka mina AlqilaAdapi maA A^aHaATa biAlEunuqi","text_ar":"حَسْبُكَ مِنَ القِلَادَةِ مَا اَحَاطَ بِالعُنُقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sufficient for thee is the necklace that surrounds the neck"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. A proverb. (TA.) Said by 'Okeyl Ibn-'Ullufeh, on his being asked why he did not censure his enemies in a longer satire. (Z.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niEomatuka qilaAdapN fiY EunuqiY laA yafuk~uhaA AlmalawaAni","text_ar":"نِعْمَتُكَ قِلَادَةٌ فِى عُنُقِى لَا يَفُكُّهَا المَلَوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy beneficence is a permanent badge upon my neck which day and night will not loose"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY fiY","text_ar":"لِى فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEonaAqihimo qalaAy^idu niEamK raAhinapN","text_ar":"اَعْنَاقِهِمْ قَلَايِدُ نِعَمٍ رَاهِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To me are owing acknowledgments required by permanent badges of favours firmly fastened upon their necks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 2]. (A.) [This use of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qlAdp","text_ar":"قلادة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a good sense is more common than the meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disgrace attaching constantly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a permanent badge of infamy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see Ham. p. 127.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaAy^idu Al$~iEori","text_ar":"قَلَايِدُ الشِّعْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqal~adaAtuhu","text_ar":"مُقَلَّدَاتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poems, that last throughout time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) See 2.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqilaAdapu","text_ar":"القِلَادَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain asterism."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["L","K","TA","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}